                        <h2>Meet Cindy Balling</h2>
                        <p>
                            Hi, I'm Cindy and I am a diabetes reversal
                            specialist! I am passionate about helping people
                            with diabetes live their best life. It has been so
                            hard for me to see many of my family members
                            struggle with diabetes. I understand what you might
                            be going through. My mission is to help everyone
                            achieve a healthy lifestyle. Please join my coaching
                            program, sign up for my regular diabetes
                            discussions, or browse around this website to learn
                            more. You can change your life and reach your goals.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            I am a lifestyle medicine coach through the American
                            College of Lifestyle Medicine. I specialize in
                            diabetes reversal and plant-based nutrition. I
                            earned my bachelor's degree in Exercise Science from
                            the University of Utah. I have experience in
                            corporate wellness, working with the developmentally
                            disabled, and with elite athletes. I can't wait to
                            meet you!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
